oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 7
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." The song "Farewell Blues" is listed on the box but is not included on this tape. The Song "Blue Rose of the Rio" is not listed on the box but is included in this recording. This is part seven of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is twenty-one of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow;
